===Etymology===
Borrowed from {{bor|en|sh|Jugoslavija}}, in turn from {{m|sh|jug||south}} and {{m|sh|slavija||''[[Slavia]]'', the land of the [[Slav]]s}}. Literally, ''the land of the southern Slavs''.

